{"text": " Exhale from the top, from the chest, from the belly, and empty yourself of air. Attention on exhalation from the nose, from the chest, from the belly. Allow your body to inhale easily into the internal emptiness. From the top, from the chest, pull the belly inward to push out the air, and empty yourself with the next exhale. Lower your attention towards the abdominal area. And with each exhale, bring your attention lower towards the belly. Pull the belly inward to push out the air, and reach the center of your belly. Exhale and connect with the center of gravity. Allow your body to inhale as desired. Continue reaching and connecting with the center of gravity with each exhale. From the nose, from the chest, pull the belly inward and stay in the center of gravity. When thought comes in, exhale from the belly, and stay in the center of gravity. Back to center.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 4.640000000000001, "end": 18.84, "text": " Exhale from the top, from the chest, from the belly, and empty yourself of air.", "tokens": [50364, 31911, 490, 264, 1192, 11, 490, 264, 7443, 11, 490, 264, 11696, 11, 293, 6707, 1803, 295, 1988, 13, 51752], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.382035960321841, "compression_ratio": 1.144927536231884, "no_speech_prob": 0.10838406533002853, "words": [{"word": " Exhale", "start": 4.640000000000001, "end": 6.040000000000001, "probability": 0.49164360761642456}, {"word": " from", "start": 6.040000000000001, "end": 7.44, "probability": 0.8157758712768555}, {"word": " the", "start": 7.44, "end": 7.64, "probability": 0.9920530319213867}, {"word": " top,", "start": 7.64, "end": 8.04, "probability": 0.968837320804596}, {"word": " from", "start": 8.96, "end": 10.32, "probability": 0.9629848003387451}, {"word": " the", "start": 10.32, "end": 10.52, "probability": 0.9963486194610596}, {"word": " chest,", "start": 10.52, "end": 11.06, "probability": 0.9934837222099304}, {"word": " from", "start": 12.02, "end": 13.36, "probabili